1196.name: Dur RU
1196.Applications: To be aplied on-armour-platings of tools and machine parts in the mining, road construction, well digging, special civil engineering, depression drilling technology, where strongest abrasion by minerals may occur.
1196.Suitable_For: Scratchers, mixers, deep drilling, mining, bentonit mixers, cement mixers, stabilisers, impellers, augers etc.
